ely accepted view to the test, had not been undertaken until now. We present two main findings that may challenge the current view of \u2425HV evolution: multiple host-switching events were observed at a higher rate than previously appreciated, and bats and primates harbor a large diversity of \u2425HVs which may have led to increased cross-species transmissions from these taxa to other mammals.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Escalera-Zamudio, Marina", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Rojas-Anaya, Edith", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Kolokotronis, Sergios-Orestis", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Taboada, Blanca", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Loza-Rubio, Elizabeth", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "M\u00e9ndez-Ojeda, Maria L.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Arias, Carlos F.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Osterrieder, Nikolaus", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Greenwood, Alex D.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Damania, Blossom", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Meng, Xiang-Jin", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/918875a18bd31c5a8062a51f80446f39", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/94faa69492192a88ced88178238dc3ace75378eb692f41f35c62594f841199ef", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/6U2WY2YU", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/6U2WY2YU", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/324d060bbe3bc5f41f3403575199a4b6!/b252094-254588", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/ce1e7618f237ff56e74d51f496e811a3", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme":